div.p: Actor B initiates process by sending to Actor A funds request

- Maria choose contact
- Maria clicks request fund
- that triggers contract function: createRequest()
- that creates request object by its struct
- emits event: requestCreated()
- event gets saved by backend app
- backend app saves a reminder for the req.: to send a push not. 1 week earlier than the deadline of the request.
- backend does push notification to each sides: Maria & Lewis
